### Bridge Blueprint

File: `mw-backend/maryland_driveway_wp_bridge_blueprint.py` (exists, uncommitted).
Registered in `server.py` lines 349-350 (uncommitted modified).
Deploy step: `git add maryland_driveway_wp_bridge_blueprint.py server.py && git commit && git push`.

Proxies `/demos/maryland-driveway-restore/*` → `http://127.0.0.1:8081/*`.
Injects `Host: api.michaelwegter.com` + `X-Forwarded-Proto: https`.

